Package: rcicrdiagnostics
Title: Data Quality Diagnostics for Reverse Correlation Experiments in Social Psychology Using the Rcicr Package
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Manuel", "Oliveira",
           email = "manuel.olivethree@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A toolkit that runs data-quality diagnostics for reverse
    correlation experiments. Supports both the standard two-image
    forced-choice (2IFC) pipeline via the 'rcicr' package (Dotsch,
    2016, 2023) and the Brief-RC pipeline (Schmitz, Rougier, &
    Yzerbyt, 2024). Designed to be run before computing classification
    images or information values so that silent data-processing errors
    are caught early.
